Package org.planit.graph

Class EdgeSegmentImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.planit.graph.EdgeSegmentImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EdgeSegment>, EdgeSegment
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConnectoidSegmentImpl, LinkSegmentImpl
    public abstract class EdgeSegmentImpl
extends Object
implements EdgeSegment
    EdgeSegment represents an edge in a particular (single) direction. Each edge has either one or two edge segments where each edge segment may have a more detailed geography than its parent link (which represents both directions via a centreline) This class is now abstract. It is extended by LinkSegment (physical links) and Connectoid (virtual links).
    Author:
    markr
